      "contents": "\n  (** ** action on morphisms of the construction of a right adjoint to [F] *)\n  "
    },
    {
      "_type": "sentence",
      "contents": "Definition right_morphism_of\n             C C' CF\n             D D' DF\n             (F : Functor C D) (G : Functor D C) (A : F -| G)\n             (F' : Functor C' D') (G' : Functor D' C') (A' : F' -| G')\n             (T : NaturalTransformation (F' o CF) (DF o F))\n  : NaturalTransformation (CF o G) (G' o DF)\n    := (@left_morphism_of _ _ DF^op _ _ CF^op F^op G^op A^op F'^op G'^op A'^op T^op)^op.",
      "messages": [],
      "goals": []
    },
    {
      "_type": "text",
      "contents": "\n\n  "
    },
    {
      "_type": "sentence",
      "contents": "Definition right_morphism_of_nondep\n             C D\n             (F : Functor C D) (G : Functor D C) (A : F -| G)\n             (F' : Functor C D) (G' : Functor D C) (A' : F' -| G')\n             (T : NaturalTransformation F' F)\n  : NaturalTransformation G G'\n    := (@left_morphism_of_nondep _ _ F^op G^op A^op F'^op G'^op A'^op T^op)^op.",
      "messages": [],
      "goals": []
    },
    {
